OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRape trials: Courts to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpilot new technology and   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftraining                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Crown Courts are to be upgraded with   
OL,6, better technology while staff will     
OL,7, receive specialist training to help    
OL,8, with rape trials, the government says. 
OL,10,FThe pilot, in Newcastle, Leeds and     
OL,11,FLondon, will see independent advisers  
OL,12,Fon hand in courts to support victims.  
OL,14,FEarlier this year, the police and court
OL,15,Fwatchdog called for specialist rape    
OL,16,Fcourts to help clear a cases backlog.  
OL,18,FOne victim, who may have to wait five  
OL,19,Fyears for her trial, said a generation 
OL,20,Fof women "have no faith" in the system.
